. // Conditional Invariant Prelect(1998) 
. program define OET_ML4
  1. args lnf sigma beta gamma eta
  2. tempvar j
  3. gen double `j'=`gamma'*exp(-`beta'*(1-winpc^`eta')/`eta')
  4. quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
  5. end

. 
. local vars1 = "$minimal"

. local vars2 = ""

. 
. ml model lf OET_ML4 (sigma:pse= `vars1' `vars2') (beta4: `vars1' `vars2') (gamma4:  `vars1' `vars2') (eta4: )
